WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: ALk5F8jsz9w

NOTE Language: en

00:00:15.940 --> 00:00:30.980
I bow to all the seekers of Truth. This song
that you are listening to has been written

00:00:30.990 --> 00:00:41.390
by a poet called Namadeva about sixteenth
century and what he’s singing there is,

00:00:41.390 --> 00:00:59.239
“Oh, Mother, give me my yoga.” Yoga means
the union with the Divine.

00:00:59.239 --> 00:01:11.070
I said I bow to you all because you’re seekers
of Truth. At the very outset, one has to know

00:01:11.070 --> 00:01:22.520
that Truth is what it is. You cannot change
it. You cannot transform it. You cannot conceptualize

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:35.130
it. And, unfortunately, at this human awareness,
you cannot know it, whatever you may try.

00:01:35.130 --> 00:01:43.440
If once we humbly understand this, that we
can go up to our mental projections and not

00:01:43.440 --> 00:01:54.690
beyond that, Truth has to be known on your
central nervous system. In the evolutionary

00:01:54.690 --> 00:02:06.750
process, whatever we have known, we have known
it on our central nervous system. For example,

00:02:06.750 --> 00:02:20.450
if you bring a dog or a horse and he sees
this beautiful hall, he won’t understand.

00:02:20.450 --> 00:02:29.620
If you take him through a dirty lane, he won’t
understand. He can just pass through. But,

00:02:29.620 --> 00:02:42.170
while we human beings have developed a kind
of a sensitivity, sensitivity to so many things.

00:02:42.170 --> 00:02:52.390
Also, we should have developed sensitivity
to spirituality, but sometimes we miss the

00:02:52.390 --> 00:02:55.950
point.

00:02:55.950 --> 00:03:08.830
Now, whatever I am going to tell should be
taken as a hypothesis, but you should have

00:03:08.830 --> 00:03:21.120
an open mind of a scientist. If it is true,
you should accept it, if you are honest and,

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:28.310
one must know that it is for the benevolence.
Your benevolence as well as the benevolence

00:03:28.310 --> 00:03:41.930
of your country and the benevolence of the
whole world. But, to understand this, I have

00:03:41.930 --> 00:03:48.569
to tell you it’s not meant for idiots and
stupid people. You have to have some amount

00:03:48.569 --> 00:03:58.510
of I.Q. to understand that we have to achieve
our selfhood, our spirit hood.

00:03:58.510 --> 00:04:05.739
What’s the matter with both of you? Why
are you laughing? Will you please go out.

00:04:05.739 --> 00:04:18.539
There’s nothing to laugh. Will you please
behave yourself.

00:04:18.539 --> 00:04:30.779
So one has to understand that evolutionary
process is absolutely free, without any effort

00:04:30.779 --> 00:04:41.509
and you can’t pay for your evolution. It
is spontaneous. Like you have this Mother

00:04:41.509 --> 00:04:52.080
Earth and you put the seed in it, then it
sprouts by itself. What do you do? Nothing.

00:04:52.080 --> 00:05:01.080
It is spontaneous and that’s what exactly
happens to you, that spontaneously you achieve

00:05:01.080 --> 00:05:05.779
that state of the spirit.

00:05:05.779 --> 00:05:14.490
When we say, “This is my body. This is my
mind. This is my ego. These are my conditionings,”

00:05:14.490 --> 00:05:21.580
we’re all the time saying “my,” but
who is this “I” to whom all these things

00:05:21.580 --> 00:05:32.240
belong? We have never questioned this. This
“I” is the spirit.

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:45.120
So the first truth is that you are the pure
spirit. And the second truth is that there

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:56.430
is all pervading power of Divine Love which
does all living work. For example, these beautiful

00:05:56.430 --> 00:06:03.669
flowers. We take them for granted. Who runs
our heart? We never ask this question. If

00:06:03.669 --> 00:06:10.259
you ask a doctor, he’ll say, “It’s an
autonomous nervous system.” Who is this

00:06:10.259 --> 00:06:15.129
auto? If you ask them, they won’t be able
to answer.

00:06:15.129 --> 00:06:22.110
So science cannot answer many questions and
one of them is that “Why are we on this

00:06:22.110 --> 00:06:31.379
Earth? What is the purpose of our life? What
is the goal of our life? What is our identity?

00:06:31.379 --> 00:06:39.219
This question is not asked and, if asked,
they cannot answer. They cannot answer this

00:06:39.219 --> 00:06:49.629
simple question, “Why are we on this Earth?”
But one has to know that we are on this Earth

00:06:49.629 --> 00:06:56.460
to become the Spirit, to enter into the Kingdom
of God. This is our purpose. That’s why

00:06:56.460 --> 00:07:06.430
we are here, and then to be the instruments
of that Divine Power, which is all-pervading.

00:07:06.430 --> 00:07:13.059
This Divine Power has been described in many
ways. Patanjali has called has called it as

00:07:13.059 --> 00:07:17.029
[check spelling: Ritambarapragya]. In the
Bible it is called as the Cool Breeze of the

00:07:17.029 --> 00:07:25.509
Holy Ghost. Also it is called as the All Pervading
Power of Divine Love. In the Koran it is called

00:07:25.509 --> 00:07:33.360
as Ruh. In the Indian scriptures it is called
as Paramchaitanya.

00:07:33.360 --> 00:07:42.330
The civilization in the West has grown very
big. It’s like a big tree outgrown its size,

00:07:42.330 --> 00:07:51.219
but we must find out our roots. I do not make
difference between East and West. So we must

00:07:51.219 --> 00:07:57.580
find out our roots, whether it comes from
East or from West. The knowledge today I’m

00:07:57.580 --> 00:08:01.649
going to tell you about is the knowledge of
our roots. We [Mother says “we”, but for

00:08:01.649 --> 00:08:03.789
clarity sake perhaps should be replaced by
“you”] have been already told about the

00:08:03.789 --> 00:08:09.509
centers and about this power that is called
as Kundalini.

00:08:09.509 --> 00:08:18.259
This power is placed in the triangular bone
which is called as sacrum, which means Greeks

00:08:18.259 --> 00:08:26.189
knew about this centre. They very well knew
about it, that’s why they called it sacred,

00:08:26.189 --> 00:08:39.190
sacrum. In many countries there has been a
manifestation that they know about this particular

00:08:39.190 --> 00:08:50.490
power. I happened to go to Colombia where
I collected an authentic antique copy of the

00:08:50.490 --> 00:09:02.060
antique necklace. The necklace had at its
bottom a Kundalini and even the earrings had

00:09:02.060 --> 00:09:16.230
the Kundalini, but, surprisingly, it was from
the Indians of America, found here with the

00:09:16.230 --> 00:09:25.910
Indians of America, though it is now kept
in the museum in Colombia. It was in America

00:09:25.910 --> 00:09:32.009
that people knew about Kundalini, definitely,
absolutely in three and a half coil they had

00:09:32.009 --> 00:09:40.029
done this pattern very well. Is very surprising
that it was done even before Columbus came

00:09:40.029 --> 00:09:43.100
here.

00:09:43.100 --> 00:09:48.709
So this knowledge was known to people, I think,
all over the world, but then gradually it

00:09:48.709 --> 00:10:00.180
subsided. Especially in India, till the twelfth
century, it was kept as a tradition just to

00:10:00.180 --> 00:10:07.180
give realization to one person, one guru and
one realization. There was not a sort of a

00:10:07.180 --> 00:10:12.850
mass realization, or anything, and they didn’t
even talk about it. They kept a secret. But

00:10:12.850 --> 00:10:22.120
in the twelfth century one great poet called
Ganyeshwara, he wrote in his book, “Ganyeshwari,”

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:28.870
sixth chapter about Kundalini. He took the
permission of his guru and he wrote it, but

00:10:28.870 --> 00:10:35.670
still they denounced it and they said that
this is something not to be read because they

00:10:35.670 --> 00:10:39.690
didn’t know how to do it. They didn’t
know how to raise the Kundalini. They didn’t

00:10:39.690 --> 00:10:44.699
know how to give realization. So the people
who were at the helm of affairs said, they

00:10:44.699 --> 00:10:49.759
denounced it, “Don’t read this chapter.”

00:10:49.759 --> 00:10:56.990
Then in the sixteenth century we had many
poets in India who have written about it,

00:10:56.990 --> 00:11:07.149
Guru Nanaka, Kabira, Ramadasa, so many of
them have written about this Kundalini awakening.

00:11:07.149 --> 00:11:13.740
Many then tantricas came up who’d write
to misuse the word and misused the whole thing

00:11:13.740 --> 00:11:18.079
and deceived people by telling them false
things.

00:11:18.079 --> 00:11:22.250
There are so many false people who came to
your country and I feel ashamed about them,

00:11:22.250 --> 00:11:27.769
those who came in this country, but also you
people are to be blamed in a way, because

00:11:27.769 --> 00:11:36.589
you should have used some discretion. When
I came first, you’ll be surprised in ’72,

00:11:36.589 --> 00:11:44.879
they asked Me funny questions. In Boston,
I was there for an interview with the television

00:11:44.879 --> 00:11:51.600
and they asked Me, not on the television,
but before that, how many Rolls Royces you

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:56.600
have?” I said, “I’ve no Rolls Royce.”
So they said, “Are you not in the business?”

00:11:56.600 --> 00:12:02.459
I said, “This is no business. This is something
else.” So they said, “We don’t believe

00:12:02.459 --> 00:12:07.389
in a person who has no business and we’ll
not give you any chance on the television.”

00:12:07.389 --> 00:12:13.819
People were so materialistic and they said,
“You are not taking any money, so it must

00:12:13.819 --> 00:12:19.870
be something hocus pocus.” So superficial
they were. I was very disappointed and I said,

00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:24.670
“I’ll never come to this country” and
I didn’t come for nine years, till some

00:12:24.670 --> 00:12:31.240
people who were here who got interests and
they told Me, “Mother, better come now.

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:38.810
Is going to be better than what you found
it in 1972.” So I came here.

00:12:38.810 --> 00:12:44.699
So one has to understand that it’s a living
process and you cannot pay for it. There’s

00:12:44.699 --> 00:12:52.100
no guarantee. There’s no guarantee, but
if you desire all of you can get your realization

00:12:52.100 --> 00:12:58.930
without any difficulty. It’s a very simple
thing that happens to you. When this Kundalini

00:12:58.930 --> 00:13:08.759
passes through these six centers, it nourishes
it, it integrates it. Also it enlightens them.

00:13:08.759 --> 00:13:15.939
By that, our physical, mental, and emotional,
spiritual problems are solved. Most of the

00:13:15.939 --> 00:13:22.470
global problems are because of human beings,
and most of the human problems are because

00:13:22.470 --> 00:13:28.360
of these chakras or these centers within us.

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:36.310
So, if you can cure these centers, you can
definitely cure human beings physically, mentally,

00:13:36.310 --> 00:13:45.110
emotionally and also spiritually. But then
it is connected. The yoga takes place with

00:13:45.110 --> 00:13:53.180
this all pervading power and the light of
the spirit shines in your attention. Then

00:13:53.180 --> 00:13:58.730
so many things happen that you are amazed
how fantastic you are. These are all your

00:13:58.730 --> 00:14:04.009
dormant powers, will start manifesting.

00:14:04.009 --> 00:14:12.069
One thing one should know that there cannot
be any gimmick about Truth. There cannot be

00:14:12.069 --> 00:14:21.569
any sort of a false pretenses about it. It
has to be straight forward and simple, but

00:14:21.569 --> 00:14:30.680
I have known people who have been doing all
kinds of things, like people paid three hundred

00:14:30.680 --> 00:14:37.249
pounds for a mantra. I mean, this, in India,
nobody would do, but thank God we are not

00:14:37.249 --> 00:14:41.490
so rich to waste our money. Three hundred
pounds for a mantra, you don’t need any

00:14:41.490 --> 00:14:53.480
guru for that, a donkey can do it also. And
then, after that, somebody says you can raise

00:14:53.480 --> 00:15:02.420
yourself from the grounds and about three
feet you can fly. Already there’s jam on

00:15:02.420 --> 00:15:05.860
the roads. Why do you want to have such people
flying at three feet? They’ll be hitting

00:15:05.860 --> 00:15:12.649
all the cars, I think. But people paid six
thousand pounds for such a nonsense. They

00:15:12.649 --> 00:15:20.329
broke their bottoms and had all kinds of problems
and they have been to Me with epilepsy. So

00:15:20.329 --> 00:15:25.360
all such stupid things people have done without
even thinking.

00:15:25.360 --> 00:15:30.339
Now there’s a new thing they have started,
showing a pendulum can move with your mind

00:15:30.339 --> 00:15:38.339
power. It’s nothing but mesmerism, simple.
But we have to know [what is] what is our

00:15:38.339 --> 00:15:45.620
value. What are we here for? What, are we
here just to move pendulums or to fly in the

00:15:45.620 --> 00:15:52.360
air? Why are we here? That’s why at the
very outset I said that Sahaja Yoga is not

00:15:52.360 --> 00:16:01.870
meant for idiotic or stupid people. It’s
a complete logical thing which is tangible.

00:16:01.870 --> 00:16:07.720
You can find out. For example, I said that
physically you are cured.

00:16:07.720 --> 00:16:16.839
Yes, of course, there are three doctors, one
of them is here, who got his M.D. in Sahaja

00:16:16.839 --> 00:16:25.499
Yoga, which showed you can cure incurable
diseases like asthma, epilepsy and also physical

00:16:25.499 --> 00:16:33.670
fitness. Three doctors got this. And there
are many doctors who are doing this research

00:16:33.670 --> 00:16:43.879
all over the world. You’ll be surprised
that in Russia there are two thousand doctors

00:16:43.879 --> 00:16:54.689
who are practicing Sahaja Yoga. I must say,
for your information, Russians are tremendously

00:16:54.689 --> 00:17:04.280
sensitive to spirituality. They threw out
all false gurus, everything. I don’t know,

00:17:04.280 --> 00:17:11.600
maybe our freedom has lead us into a mess
like this. Freedom without discretion can

00:17:11.600 --> 00:17:19.839
be very dangerous. That may be the reason
we are now finding lost, as far as our society

00:17:19.839 --> 00:17:26.190
is concerned, as far as our children are concerned.
In every way, we are confused.

00:17:26.190 --> 00:17:35.050
But there’s a way out from all this which
is very simple and the way out is that your

00:17:35.050 --> 00:17:44.490
Kundalini is to be awakened. That’s very
simple, I told you, because it is built in.

00:17:44.490 --> 00:17:54.640
It’s your own power that is going to work
it out. No obligation. There’s no commitment,

00:17:54.640 --> 00:18:02.590
nothing. As far as you are a human being,
that is sufficient because you are at the

00:18:02.590 --> 00:18:10.850
epitome of evolution. We do not know our value.
We don’t even think why God made us human

00:18:10.850 --> 00:18:17.270
beings. We just accept ourselves as human
beings, but there are so many problems and

00:18:17.270 --> 00:18:22.490
so many confusions that we don’t understand
what’s going on.

00:18:22.490 --> 00:18:29.240
One of the reasons is that we do not know
the absolute Truth. Somebody says this is

00:18:29.240 --> 00:18:33.630
right, another says that is right. Somebody
says this is right and they’re fighting.

00:18:33.630 --> 00:18:40.920
They believe in it. They believe that this
is right, that is right and they fight. All

00:18:40.920 --> 00:18:53.500
kinds of wrong ideas have been managed to
exploit us, to befool us and to lead us into

00:18:53.500 --> 00:19:01.370
the path of destruction. We are getting destroyed
from within, if you see. All kinds of diseases,

00:19:01.370 --> 00:19:10.410
unknown diseases are coming up. Our children
are getting ruined. Families are getting ruined.

00:19:10.410 --> 00:19:15.650
What is the reason for this decline? Within
these thirty, forty years only such a decline

00:19:15.650 --> 00:19:24.860
has come. What is the reason? The reason is,
one of them is that our indiscrete freedom.

00:19:24.860 --> 00:19:26.820
And a second one, I think, is materialism.

00:19:26.820 --> 00:19:32.550
As I told you, they asked Me for a Rolls Royce
because they can’t understand anything without

00:19:32.550 --> 00:19:41.620
money. This is the most absurd thing that
they believe that spirituality also can be

00:19:41.620 --> 00:19:50.390
bought with money. You can purchase your guru.
You can retain him. You cannot.

00:19:50.390 --> 00:20:01.630
So what happens to you when you get your realization
is first you feel a Cool Breeze on your fingertips.

00:20:01.630 --> 00:20:09.680
Also you feel a Cool Breeze coming out of
your fontanelle bone area, which is the actualization

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:17.550
of your baptism. It’s actualization. And
Sahaja Yoga is becoming, it is not just a

00:20:17.550 --> 00:20:26.610
lecture or explanation or a sermon. It is
becoming. Means you become something that

00:20:26.610 --> 00:20:34.660
is already described that you are to be born
again. Now, if you just certify yourself as

00:20:34.660 --> 00:20:41.250
born again, you are not. It’s just a false
certificate. If you are born again, you have

00:20:41.250 --> 00:20:50.450
certain powers and you become a saint. You
have to be a saint if you are born again.

00:20:50.450 --> 00:20:56.390
You become a Sufi, but if that doesn’t happen
to you, you cannot just certify yourself as

00:20:56.390 --> 00:21:04.270
born again. Any certificate are like this.
It’s just a brand. For example, it might

00:21:04.270 --> 00:21:14.890
be a Hindu, Muslim, Christian; any one can
commit any sin. It’s just a brand. It’s

00:21:14.890 --> 00:21:16.940
nothing inside.

00:21:16.940 --> 00:21:24.190
So what happens to you that you become a righteous
person, you become you can’t do wrong things.

00:21:24.190 --> 00:21:31.880
You cannot do things which are irreligious.
You just don’t do it. You don’t get tempted

00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:39.250
to do anything. On the contrary, you enjoy
your virtues. Your attention becomes absolutely

00:21:39.250 --> 00:21:47.190
innocent, without any lust and greed. And
such a person, even a glance of such a person

00:21:47.190 --> 00:21:48.170
can bring peace.

00:21:48.170 --> 00:21:58.170
The source of all this is this All Pervading
Power of Divine Love. So you are connected

00:21:58.170 --> 00:22:03.970
with that power. Once you are connected with
that power, it starts flowing through and

00:22:03.970 --> 00:22:15.950
when it starts flowing through you, you can
feel it. Then it makes you grow. As a result,

00:22:15.950 --> 00:22:23.060
you know the Absolute Truth on your fingertips.
Even children can know the Absolute Truth

00:22:23.060 --> 00:22:29.060
on their fingertips. There are people who
don’t believe in God. They come to Me. I

00:22:29.060 --> 00:22:33.830
say, “All right, ask the question, ‘Is
there God?’ three times” and they get

00:22:33.830 --> 00:22:39.790
the Cool Breeze. Then I’ll [say] “Just
say, ‘There is God.'” Then they get a

00:22:39.790 --> 00:22:48.250
tremendous stream of Cool Breeze. Thus, you
can make out also your own centers, what’s

00:22:48.250 --> 00:22:53.650
wrong with your own centers. Is there any
problem in your centre? Immediately you can

00:22:53.650 --> 00:22:57.980
find out on the fingertips.

00:22:57.980 --> 00:23:09.410
Many people who are about to go for a heart
attack or for some sort of a serious cancer,

00:23:09.410 --> 00:23:14.440
do not know they have. But a Sahaja Yogi will
immediately know that on his centre is catching

00:23:14.440 --> 00:23:22.500
and immediately he knows also how to correct
it. So you can have self-knowledge about your

00:23:22.500 --> 00:23:24.910
own centers and you understand.

00:23:24.910 --> 00:23:31.070
Today only, one gentleman came and told Me,
“Mother, my Agnya is catching. Means that

00:23:31.070 --> 00:23:36.490
I’m egotistical.” Nobody would say that,
“I’m egoistical,” but he just came and

00:23:36.490 --> 00:23:41.270
told Me, “Mother, my Agyna’s catching.
Please correct me.” That means yourself

00:23:41.270 --> 00:23:46.580
knows that this is happening within yourself
and you know how to correct yourself, so you

00:23:46.580 --> 00:23:54.310
become the doctor, you become diagnosis and
you become the medicine. It sounds very fantastic,

00:23:54.310 --> 00:23:56.480
but it’s a fact.

00:23:56.480 --> 00:24:00.960
Then the second thing happens to you that
you get the knowledge about other’s centers

00:24:00.960 --> 00:24:07.150
also. You know about others. Sitting down
here you can find out what are the centers

00:24:07.150 --> 00:24:13.980
of any person. Immediately you can find out.
Once you find out the centers, if you know

00:24:13.980 --> 00:24:19.470
how to correct them, you can correct also
others. So who is the other? The microcosm

00:24:19.470 --> 00:24:23.280
becomes the macrocosm.

00:24:23.280 --> 00:24:31.560
Then we have another problem always that we
live in the future or in the past, never in

00:24:31.560 --> 00:24:36.470
the present. If I say come to your present,
you cannot come. It’s very difficult for

00:24:36.470 --> 00:24:43.230
you to come to your present. So what’s the
reason is that we are thinking of the future

00:24:43.230 --> 00:24:49.510
and the past. One thought rises and falls
down. Another thought rises and falls down.

00:24:49.510 --> 00:24:57.740
In between these thoughts there is this vilumba
[check spelling], is what we call the present.

00:24:57.740 --> 00:25:06.470
When the Kundalini rises, she elongates the
thoughts and this space increases and you

00:25:06.470 --> 00:25:14.520
become thoughtlessly aware, thoughtlessly
aware. You become, again I say you become.

00:25:14.520 --> 00:25:19.870
There are no thoughts, but you are absolutely
aware which is also described by Jung that

00:25:19.870 --> 00:25:26.900
after realization you become thoughtlessly
aware.

00:25:26.900 --> 00:25:33.170
That is the time you are absolutely at peace
with yourself and with everything else. That’s

00:25:33.170 --> 00:25:40.320
the time you are peaceful in the real sense
of the word. I’ve seen people getting many

00:25:40.320 --> 00:25:48.720
awards, peace awards, of peace conferences
and all that. I know them, but, surprisingly,

00:25:48.720 --> 00:25:53.300
they’re extremely hot tempered and if you
have to talk to them, also you have to take

00:25:53.300 --> 00:25:57.130
a barge pole in between because they have
such a temper. I don’t know how they got

00:25:57.130 --> 00:26:02.990
these peace awards and things like that, but
you find them all around, such people who

00:26:02.990 --> 00:26:05.850
have got peace award without any peace within.

00:26:05.850 --> 00:26:12.570
So you have to have your peace within yourself
and this you achieve through thoughtless awareness.

00:26:12.570 --> 00:26:18.890
Then another thing happens to you that you
become the witness, the witness of the whole

00:26:18.890 --> 00:26:27.250
drama. Say, if you are in the water and there
are waves, you’re afraid of it. But supposing

00:26:27.250 --> 00:26:38.130
you get into the boat, then you watch these
very carefully you can watch them. Also, you

00:26:38.130 --> 00:26:46.100
can enjoy them. But supposing you know how
to swim, then you can jump and save many people.

00:26:46.100 --> 00:26:52.860
So like this, into two stages, you rise. The
first one, when you rise into the boat when

00:26:52.860 --> 00:26:58.990
you are thoughtlessly aware and the second
stage, which we call is a doubtless awareness,

00:26:58.990 --> 00:27:08.390
which is called as Sanskrit language it is
called as Nirvikalpa samadhi the first one

00:27:08.390 --> 00:27:14.670
as Nirvichar samadhi and the second one as
Nirvikalpa samadhi where you have no doubts

00:27:14.670 --> 00:27:22.380
about yourself. You know that. You know all
your inner knowledge. You know about your

00:27:22.380 --> 00:27:26.770
inner being and you know about the inner beings
of others.

00:27:26.770 --> 00:27:33.760
This knowledge we have to know and it takes
hardly any time for you to know, hardly I

00:27:33.760 --> 00:27:44.510
would say, even one month is sufficient. But
what I’ve seen that people have to be deep

00:27:44.510 --> 00:27:51.150
to go into it. Normally, once they get realization,
they feel extremely relaxed, peaceful, then

00:27:51.150 --> 00:27:59.940
finished. But it’s like a seed being sprouted.
It has to grow into a tree. They get lost

00:27:59.940 --> 00:28:04.090
first some disease they have is cured, then
they come out with another disease second

00:28:04.090 --> 00:28:11.990
year I come back. So one has to be determined
about it in the beginning. Then you cannot

00:28:11.990 --> 00:28:17.520
leave it because you enjoy it so much. You
know that you are now in the Kingdom of God.

00:28:17.520 --> 00:28:38.710
When I was in Russia there was this coupe
going on. I asked the Russians, I said, “Aren’t

00:28:38.710 --> 00:28:55.840
you… [Interruption in recording]

00:28:55.840 --> 00:29:07.820
The another thing that happens to you, that
you jump into the Ocean of Joy. So far we

00:29:07.820 --> 00:29:14.730
have never known Joy. We have happiness and
unhappiness. Whatever pampers our ego, we’ll

00:29:14.730 --> 00:29:20.260
feel happy or which gives us some emotional
satisfaction, we’ll feel happy and then

00:29:20.260 --> 00:29:30.630
we feel unhappy. So we jump from one to another.
But with this, we are in the Ocean of Joy.

00:29:30.630 --> 00:29:33.340
Now we’ll [should be changed to “you’ll]
be surprised that Sahaja Yoga is working in

00:29:33.340 --> 00:29:39.970
fifty-five nations. I’m sorry, to Philadelphia
I have come for the first time. I wanted to

00:29:39.970 --> 00:29:47.010
come, but I was so disappointed when I came
here in ’72. We are only four people for

00:29:47.010 --> 00:29:52.470
the program. Such a big hall and four people
sitting there, so I said, “Better not go

00:29:52.470 --> 00:29:58.480
to Philadelphia. May be the same style.”
And these out of these four people, the other

00:29:58.480 --> 00:30:03.830
day one gentleman came and told Me that, “You
cure my father’s eyesight in 1972.” I

00:30:03.830 --> 00:30:09.020
said, “Maybe, I don’t remember all that,”
but he was one of them who came.

00:30:09.020 --> 00:30:16.270
So you can imagine how now the awareness for
spirituality is growing. You see so many people

00:30:16.270 --> 00:30:24.220
now. So many people that I’m amazed Myself
this year what has happened suddenly that

00:30:24.220 --> 00:30:30.660
where only we were getting only four or seven
people, suddenly we have so many people. While

00:30:30.660 --> 00:30:38.520
they use to go to all kinds of false gurus,
pay them money and get injured or get into

00:30:38.520 --> 00:30:43.970
recluseness or all kinds of things would happen
to them. But this time I was surprised, all

00:30:43.970 --> 00:30:51.280
over America there’s a kind of an awakening
and people are becoming more alert about it.

00:30:51.280 --> 00:30:57.200
All these things happen to you for which you
don’t have to pay. For all the knowledge,

00:30:57.200 --> 00:31:05.610
you don’t have to pay. You have just attend
our collectivity, means we have our centers,

00:31:05.610 --> 00:31:12.600
so please come to our centers and where they
will give you all the knowledge about it.

00:31:12.600 --> 00:31:18.490
You can master it, maximum, within one month’s
time. You just become masters.

00:31:18.490 --> 00:31:23.340
Now you may say, “Mother, it is very fantastic
to hear about ourselves, but you don’t know

00:31:23.340 --> 00:31:32.320
how fantastic you are. Like you take a small
little box of a television to some remote

00:31:32.320 --> 00:31:39.390
village. All the people will say, “What
is this? It is just a box?” Why, you tell

00:31:39.390 --> 00:31:46.310
them that there is going to be you can easily
see lots of films in it. They won’t believe.

00:31:46.310 --> 00:31:55.320
Once it is connected only that they’ll be
amazed at the television, the way it is showing

00:31:55.320 --> 00:32:02.450
all kinds of things because it is built-in
and also it is built-in in you. All this is

00:32:02.450 --> 00:32:13.190
there which is within you, which you can easily
verify it. It’s absolutely tangible and

00:32:13.190 --> 00:32:19.750
then you know the value of your life and then
you know the purpose of your life.

00:32:19.750 --> 00:32:24.710
This is what it is. In this short time, I
don’t know how much I can tell you about

00:32:24.710 --> 00:32:33.360
it. Now, you have here beautiful lights and
beautifully they’re lit up. You have to

00:32:33.360 --> 00:32:43.180
use only one switch. It all comes up. If I
have to tell you the history of electricity,

00:32:43.180 --> 00:32:50.120
how it came to this country, then to your
city and all that, it would be very boring.

00:32:50.120 --> 00:32:53.400
But if it is built-in, why not have the light?

00:32:53.400 --> 00:33:00.660
So, I would say that you should have the light
and you should know what you are. First you

00:33:00.660 --> 00:33:06.430
get that light and then we will see about
the rest of the knowledge. That you can easily

00:33:06.430 --> 00:33:11.980
get when you go to our centers and they will
give you. I have to confess that we don’t

00:33:11.980 --> 00:33:18.400
take any money, so we do not have elaborate
places like Taj Mahal to have our programs.

00:33:18.400 --> 00:33:25.280
It’s simple abodes and in simple places
you have to come with a simple mind to achieve

00:33:25.280 --> 00:33:26.860
your spiritual life.

00:33:26.860 --> 00:33:38.990
That’s what it is today. I do not know that
what it is to, that we are now in the blossom

00:33:38.990 --> 00:33:46.690
time, as I call it, because many flowers are
born and they are to become the fruits. This

00:33:46.690 --> 00:33:52.760
is the resurrection time, which is described
in all the scriptures. But it’s not like

00:33:52.760 --> 00:33:58.560
this, the way they had described us, something
wrong with them, that all the dead bodies

00:33:58.560 --> 00:34:04.520
who are in the graves will come out of the
graves. I mean, how much is left out of them,

00:34:04.520 --> 00:34:10.730
God knows. Must be some bones or maybe some
skulls there. So they’ll come out of the

00:34:10.730 --> 00:34:16.260
graves and they will get their resurrection.
This is a very wrong idea.

00:34:16.260 --> 00:34:22.129
Once I happened to meet a fellow, a Muslim
from Bosnia and he told Me “I want to die

00:34:22.129 --> 00:34:29.540
for my religion, for God’s sake.” I said,
“But why? Who told you to die?” He said,

00:34:29.540 --> 00:34:34.450
“Now, if I die in the name of God, I’ll
be resurrected.” I said, “It’s all wrong.

00:34:34.450 --> 00:34:39.159
That’s not the way it is going to work out.
Resurrection is going to work out this way.

00:34:39.159 --> 00:34:45.310
That at this time, all these souls will take
their birth. All these souls will take their

00:34:45.310 --> 00:34:50.810
birth and they will be resurrected as human
beings they’ll have to come.” That’s

00:34:50.810 --> 00:35:00.850
why we find all kinds of funny people these
days, all kinds of cruel, criminal, all kinds

00:35:00.850 --> 00:35:10.910
of idiotic, stupid, I mean very queer, weird
funny ideas which find such, such a variety

00:35:10.910 --> 00:35:20.970
of people and such a tremendous population
that we should understand they have to have

00:35:20.970 --> 00:35:26.830
their chance of resurrection. But how many
will come? That’s the point. How many are

00:35:26.830 --> 00:35:28.070
going to come?

00:35:28.070 --> 00:35:34.040
Now, see, in your Philadelphia there are so
many people. How many are here and how many

00:35:34.040 --> 00:35:38.760
are going to get realization and how many
are going to settle down? Depends on their

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:44.580
wisdom and depends on their understanding
of spirituality. If they don’t have, you

00:35:44.580 --> 00:35:51.690
cannot force on them. You cannot force Self
Realization on them. Never. It has to be accepted.

00:35:51.690 --> 00:35:58.830
In their own freedom, they have to ask for
it. It cannot be forced. This power that you

00:35:58.830 --> 00:36:06.980
see is a power of pure desire. If you don’t
have pure desire, it won’t rise, all other

00:36:06.980 --> 00:36:14.830
desires are such that they’re never satiable
in general, so this desire that you have within.

00:36:14.830 --> 00:36:20.080
You may be aware of it or you may not be,
but it is there and once it is awakened, such

00:36:20.080 --> 00:36:26.780
a satisfaction settles in you. You are very
satisfied with yourself and life becomes so

00:36:26.780 --> 00:36:34.280
beautiful. And the friendship [and the] because
I heard this is a brotherly and a sisterly

00:36:34.280 --> 00:36:40.780
place. I was very happy to hear that. That
is what exactly Sahaja Yoga is, such love.

00:36:40.780 --> 00:36:45.760
Now I told you there are fifty five nations
which are following Sahaja Yoga, but when

00:36:45.760 --> 00:36:51.580
you see one Sahaja Yogis meeting another one,
I mean, you really feel, “What is this?

00:36:51.580 --> 00:36:58.240
How it is happening? How they are achieving
it?” It’s not easy to understand such

00:36:58.240 --> 00:37:05.850
love, such pure love. We never had any case
of flirting or any case of any woman running

00:37:05.850 --> 00:37:10.920
away with some another husband or something.
It’s never seen that. They’re so innocent

00:37:10.920 --> 00:37:17.310
and so simple. Just like children they become
and the way they behave towards each other

00:37:17.310 --> 00:37:23.820
is beautiful to see. This is a new race of
angels. My husband always said that, “I

00:37:23.820 --> 00:37:28.630
know You are an angel. You are something great.
But I don’t think you can make others.”

00:37:28.630 --> 00:37:33.560
He was sure about it. Now he says that “I
have to believe” and I have to say, yes,

00:37:33.560 --> 00:37:38.630
it is so because if you have to be honest,
you see those things. You all can become [unclear:

00:37:38.630 --> 00:37:44.380
that]. Just have self-confidence about it,
that you all can become that, all these powers

00:37:44.380 --> 00:37:49.770
are within you and that nobody can take away
these powers from you.

00:37:49.770 --> 00:37:57.350
Now, I don’t know, I find people who like
to ask Me questions. I don’t mind answering

00:37:57.350 --> 00:38:02.310
any number of questions, but I must tell you
for the last twenty-three years I have been

00:38:02.310 --> 00:38:10.600
doing this job. I know how to answer all questions.
I am quite an expert. But it’s a mental

00:38:10.600 --> 00:38:16.630
acrobat. What’s the use? It’s a mental
acrobat. If you ask Me questions, I’ll answer,

00:38:16.630 --> 00:38:23.200
no doubt. I’m quite good at it. But the
best thing is first to get the light. After

00:38:23.200 --> 00:38:31.530
getting the light, then you see for yourself
and understand that it is all there. But if

00:38:31.530 --> 00:38:37.450
you want, should we ask them to ask questions?
It’s better. About fifteen minutes are still

00:38:37.450 --> 00:38:38.070
there.

00:38:38.070 --> 00:38:40.560
Shri Mataji: Yes, please.

00:38:40.560 --> 00:38:44.300
[Man asks: “Did you advocate meditation?”]

00:38:44.300 --> 00:38:53.270
Shri Mataji: No, please be seated. It’s
very good question. You see, meditation cannot

00:38:53.270 --> 00:39:01.110
be done. You are in meditation. When you are
thoughtlessly aware, you are in meditation,

00:39:01.110 --> 00:39:05.830
otherwise we say we are doing meditation.
You can’t do it. You have to go beyond the

00:39:05.830 --> 00:39:12.100
mind, then you are in a meditative condition.
So, there is meditation, but where you have

00:39:12.100 --> 00:39:15.760
to become thoughtlessly aware.

00:39:15.760 --> 00:39:32.340
[A man asks a question.] [A yogi speaks to
Shri Mataji in Hindi.]

00:39:32.340 --> 00:39:33.880
Shri Mataji: Oh, very good. What a nice question.
That’s a seeker. That’s a seeker.

00:39:33.880 --> 00:39:34.080
Yes, Sir.

00:39:34.080 --> 00:39:46.070
[A man asks a question and a yogi explains;
“He’s talking about the channel of desire.

00:39:46.070 --> 00:39:50.950
Channel of desire. Go ahead.”]

00:39:50.950 --> 00:39:57.040
[The man continues his questions.]

00:39:57.040 --> 00:40:05.250
[Yogi: “He wants to know about the different
types of desires, the desires that relate

00:40:05.250 --> 00:40:05.750
-“]
Shri Mataji: The different types of

00:40:05.750 --> 00:40:10.970
[Yogi continues: “- the worldly desires
and the spiritual desires, how would you differentiate?”]

00:40:10.970 --> 00:40:16.450
{The man continues to speak.]

00:40:16.450 --> 00:40:17.880
[Yogi: “He’s mixed up.”]

00:40:17.880 --> 00:40:19.320
Shri Mataji: All right.

00:40:19.320 --> 00:40:21.860
[The same man asks, “And how is this related
to bhakti?”]

00:40:21.860 --> 00:40:22.630
[Yogi: “He’s asking about the relationship
of desires to bhakti.”]

00:40:22.630 --> 00:40:22.790
Desires to -?

00:40:22.790 --> 00:40:22.940
[Yogi: “Bhakti.”]

00:40:22.940 --> 00:40:23.490
Shri Mataji: All right. Please be seated.

00:40:23.490 --> 00:40:28.590
Shri Mataji: So I’ll answer your first question,
the second question first bhakti. We are doing

00:40:28.590 --> 00:40:35.700
bhakti now, of God. Without connection, what
is the bhakti? It’s like a telephone. Without

00:40:35.700 --> 00:40:40.310
connection, you’re telephoning to God, He
doesn’t listen to you. Many people come

00:40:40.310 --> 00:40:44.760
to Me. They say, “Mother, I have done so
much bhakti of Shri Krishna, but my throat

00:40:44.760 --> 00:40:50.150
is bad and I’ve got cancer of the throat.
If you say Shri Krishna looks after the throat,

00:40:50.150 --> 00:40:56.630
why is it?” Because you’re not yet connected.
If you’re not connected, what’s the use

00:40:56.630 --> 00:40:59.860
of doing bhakti. Simple thing, extremely simple.

00:40:59.860 --> 00:41:01.910
Shri Mataji: What was the first question?

00:41:01.910 --> 00:41:05.920
[Yogi: “The different types of desires,
the worldly desires and the spiritual desires.”]

00:41:05.920 --> 00:41:10.230
Shri Mataji: All right. Now people are saying
that you must give up this, you must give

00:41:10.230 --> 00:41:15.480
up that. There’s nothing to be given up.
If you give up, still you’ll stick on to

00:41:15.480 --> 00:41:21.420
that. I’ve known people who are very much
stuck, but they think they have given up.

00:41:21.420 --> 00:41:27.680
Like, I’ll tell you, some people came to
see Me. They wanted to use our ships for some

00:41:27.680 --> 00:41:36.180
purpose and they said that “We have”,
they came in an ascetic dress and they said,

00:41:36.180 --> 00:41:41.450
“Mother, you are suppose to be a holy person,
but you are sitting in all luxury and all

00:41:41.450 --> 00:41:48.160
this. How are you a holy person? We have given
up our houses. We have given up our cars,

00:41:48.160 --> 00:41:56.700
given up this, given up that.” I said, “All
right, in this house or anything which is

00:41:56.700 --> 00:42:08.100
with Me is equal to the dust particle of God
Almighty, of His Feet. You can pick up anything,

00:42:08.100 --> 00:42:18.600
but should be equal.” They started looking
around. They have not given up anything. They

00:42:18.600 --> 00:42:25.540
have given up stones. A detachment develops
within yourself.

00:42:25.540 --> 00:42:31.390
I don’t know if you have heard the story
of Raja Janaka, whose guru was Ashtabhakar

00:42:31.390 --> 00:42:41.770
[check spelling]. Raja Janaka was the father-in-law
of Shri Ram. This Raja Janaka was a king and

00:42:41.770 --> 00:42:47.950
all the saints use to bow to him, so one fellow
asked his guru, “Why is it you bow to this

00:42:47.950 --> 00:42:55.500
king? He is a king and what is so great?”
He said, “He’s the only one who can give

00:42:55.500 --> 00:42:58.360
realization and he’s so high.”

00:42:58.360 --> 00:43:05.440
So he sent one of his disciples, his name
was Nachikita [check spelling] to Raja Janaka.

00:43:05.440 --> 00:43:10.720
Raja Janaka told him, “No, you can ask anything,
but I’ll not give you self realization.”

00:43:10.720 --> 00:43:16.350
He said, “No, Sir, I must have it. But I
want to know about myself.” So he said,

00:43:16.350 --> 00:43:22.950
“All right.” So first he took him with
himself to have a bath in the river. I mean

00:43:22.950 --> 00:43:30.340
many tests he took, but lastly. And there
he was having his bath while people came and

00:43:30.340 --> 00:43:36.770
told that “Sir”, he was meditating. He
was in thoughtless awareness, just enjoying

00:43:36.770 --> 00:43:46.230
himself. And they came and told that “Your
palace is on fire.” Still he was meditating.

00:43:46.230 --> 00:43:52.340
Then they came and told him that “Now all
the family is running away from the palace.”

00:43:52.340 --> 00:43:58.180
Still he was meditating. Then they said, “The
fire is coming here and will burn everything

00:43:58.180 --> 00:44:06.380
that you have.” Now this fellow ran out
and he clutched his clothes because he thought,

00:44:06.380 --> 00:44:14.880
“This will be all burned.” But he was
still meditating. And then when he opened

00:44:14.880 --> 00:44:22.630
his eyes, he saw nothing has happened. “I
know nothing has happened. And it’s nothing

00:44:22.630 --> 00:44:24.910
important to me.”

00:44:24.910 --> 00:44:32.860
So the detachment is within. It’s not without.
You don’t have to announce it. It is within.

00:44:32.860 --> 00:44:44.070
It’s something that you do everything. As
I knew, I am a grandmother, I’m a mother,

00:44:44.070 --> 00:44:50.660
I’m a wife. My husband was holding a very
big position, all that. I did everything,

00:44:50.660 --> 00:44:58.460
but there’s a kind of a detachment about
it and this detachment can only be possible

00:44:58.460 --> 00:45:08.110
if you develop your spiritual powers. When
your spirit shines, you see everything is

00:45:08.110 --> 00:45:16.520
useless and fruitless, but by giving up things,
by renouncing things, you’re just pampering

00:45:16.520 --> 00:45:20.520
your ego by saying, “I have given up this.
I have given up that.”

00:45:20.520 --> 00:45:29.960
The other day I met a Buddhist who was a seeker.
He was all shaved off. His hair was shaved

00:45:29.960 --> 00:45:36.690
off. And he said, “Mother, I am not only
shaved off, but I am now a bankrupt.” I

00:45:36.690 --> 00:45:43.670
said, “Why?” “Because I was giving all
my money, everything to this Buddhist organization

00:45:43.670 --> 00:45:50.820
and now I’m bankrupt and I don’t know
what to do with myself.” I said “how can

00:45:50.820 --> 00:46:00.970
you pay”? God doesn’t understand money.
No.” He doesn’t understand banking. It’s

00:46:00.970 --> 00:46:05.880
your headache. You have made money. You have
made banks. You have made these houses. What

00:46:05.880 --> 00:46:12.500
is there if you give up or don’t give up?
What difference does it make? It’s your

00:46:12.500 --> 00:46:15.580
doing. All right?

00:46:15.580 --> 00:46:23.670
So the detachment must come from within and
that is so automatic. It’s a state which

00:46:23.670 --> 00:46:25.960
we have to achieve in our evolution.

00:46:25.960 --> 00:46:52.720
[Shri Mataji speaks to a Yogi in Hindi. Another
question is asked by a man in the audience.

00:46:52.720 --> 00:47:35.000
It concerns his wife and a mantra she was
given by a false guru. The wife also gets

00:47:35.000 --> 00:47:45.640
burning sensations on her fingertips…The
question is translated to Shri Mataji.]

00:47:45.640 --> 00:47:49.010
Shri Mataji: If she’s saying mantras, she
should not say. You see, mantras, please be

00:47:49.010 --> 00:47:56.030
seated, I’ll tell you. Mantras are, there’s
a science about it. You must know what centre

00:47:56.030 --> 00:48:01.510
is out of gear, which mantra to be said for
which center. It is not at random like you

00:48:01.510 --> 00:48:05.690
take out the whole Pandora box and start taking
all the medicines. No. You must know everything

00:48:05.690 --> 00:48:12.490
and if her fingers are burning it’s not
a very good sign and I wish she would had

00:48:12.490 --> 00:48:28.450
come here, I would have seen to her. But where
is the [Interruption in recording]

00:48:28.450 --> 00:48:38.280
Shri Mataji: Is it on the left hand or right
hand? [The man answers.]

00:48:38.280 --> 00:48:44.280
[Yogi: “…she’s asking was the burning
on the left hand or the right hand?]

00:48:44.280 --> 00:48:47.520
[Man: “I don’t know. I cannot -“]

00:48:47.520 --> 00:48:52.630
[Yogi: “He doesn’t know” and speaks
in Hindi.]

00:48:52.630 --> 00:49:04.680
Shri Mataji: You see, I don’t want to say
anything, but something wrong with the guru

00:49:04.680 --> 00:49:09.070
himself, I think. I’m sorry.

00:49:09.070 --> 00:49:13.460
[Shri Mataji speaks in Hindi.]

00:49:13.460 --> 00:49:16.090
Shri Mataji: Yes?

00:49:16.090 --> 00:49:20.480
[A woman asks a question.]

00:49:20.480 --> 00:49:24.869
[Shri Mataji speaks in Hindi.]

00:49:24.869 --> 00:49:31.890
[Yogi: “…She’s praying for his enlightenment
and vision….”]

00:49:31.890 --> 00:49:42.070
Shri Mataji: All right, very good idea, but
I have so many children here. Alright? Good.

00:49:42.070 --> 00:49:59.040
[Man: “Would you further explain this thoughtless
awareness and is it the same as mindful awareness

00:49:59.040 --> 00:49:59.640
of the Buddhist philosophy?]

00:49:59.640 --> 00:50:01.430
[Yogi: “The difference between thoughtless
awareness and mindful awareness.”]

00:50:01.430 --> 00:50:06.810
Shri Mataji: It’s the same, but you see,
Buddhism is very confused as every religion

00:50:06.810 --> 00:50:14.200
has been, very much confused and so I do not
know what they are thinking about it, but

00:50:14.200 --> 00:50:18.859
it’s the same thing. Is the same thing as
thoughtless awareness, should be the same

00:50:18.859 --> 00:50:29.030
thing and also many things Buddha has said
have been misused and have been, I should

00:50:29.030 --> 00:50:35.220
say, quite twisted also. So to understand
Buddhism, you take to Sahaja Yoga first. Once

00:50:35.220 --> 00:50:40.400
you get your realizations, Sir, you’ll understand
Buddhism much better in the sense that it

00:50:40.400 --> 00:50:45.700
should not be Buddhism, but it is Buddha’s
Bodha. “Bodha” means to know on your central

00:50:45.700 --> 00:50:50.980
nervous system. You become a Buddha, yourself.
You become, yourself, an enlightened person.

00:50:50.980 --> 00:50:51.250
Alright?

00:50:51.250 --> 00:50:52.090
Now, what’s it?

00:50:52.090 --> 00:51:03.350
[A man asks, “Could you please say what
the dangers are associated with Kundalini

00:51:03.350 --> 00:51:03.590
meditation.”]

00:51:03.590 --> 00:51:05.730
[Yogi: “He’s asking about any dangers
of Kundalini meditation.”]

00:51:05.730 --> 00:51:09.770
Shri Mataji: No, no, No, no. Not at all, not
at all; She’s your mother. She’s your

00:51:09.770 --> 00:51:15.040
individual mother, who gives you your second
birth. She knows everything about you. She

00:51:15.040 --> 00:51:22.210
has recorded everything and she does it very
gently. See, when you were born, your mother

00:51:22.210 --> 00:51:30.230
took all the pains upon herself, isn’t it?
And in the same way, this Kundalini does the

00:51:30.230 --> 00:51:35.490
job. But people are frightened because perhaps
maybe they don’t want, it’s an evil force

00:51:35.490 --> 00:51:39.450
I think, those who are frightened against
Kundalini because they don’t know how to

00:51:39.450 --> 00:51:49.540
do it or maybe they don’t want people to
achieve their realization. I can’t understand.

00:51:49.540 --> 00:51:56.930
Those people, as I was telling you today,
in the sixteen century Guru Nanaka, then Kabira

00:51:56.930 --> 00:52:02.930
and all these others, Ramadasa, Tukarama,
all of them, nobody has said it’s dangerous.

00:52:02.930 --> 00:52:09.450
On the contrary, Ramadasa was asked, “How
much time does it take for Kundalini to rise?”

00:52:09.450 --> 00:52:14.820
He used the word in Sanskrit, “Takshana,
that’s the moment, that moment,” he said.

00:52:14.820 --> 00:52:22.820
“Takshana, that moment.” So, But,” he
said, “there’s a condition. The one who

00:52:22.820 --> 00:52:33.490
wants should be anxious to have it and the
one who gives should be an authority, not

00:52:33.490 --> 00:52:41.310
an authority from some university or anything,
but authority in spirituality.”

00:52:41.310 --> 00:52:42.270
Yes.

00:52:42.270 --> 00:52:58.510
[A man asks a question concerning the position
a person must be in order to get Kundalini

00:52:58.510 --> 00:52:59.460
awakening.]

00:52:59.460 --> 00:53:05.180
Shri Mataji: What is it?

00:53:05.180 --> 00:53:09.350
[The question is repeated to Shri Mataji by
a yogi.]

00:53:09.350 --> 00:53:16.930
Shri Mataji: No, you see, it is all right.
You can do it, but why do all that? You have

00:53:16.930 --> 00:53:21.770
to be comfortably sitting in your chair and
you’ll get your Realization. You don’t

00:53:21.770 --> 00:53:23.750
have to go to Himalayas to stand on your head.
Just simple way.

00:53:23.750 --> 00:53:23.950
Yes, sir.

00:53:23.950 --> 00:53:31.350
[Another man asks, “What does the process
entail?” which is repeated to Shri Mataji

00:53:31.350 --> 00:53:34.490
in Hindi.]

00:53:34.490 --> 00:53:46.210
Shri Mataji: It’s Sahaj. It’s spontaneous.
Is like any living process. Alright?

00:53:46.210 --> 00:53:57.510
[A man asks, “Why is there so much heartache
and grief when you fall in love?”]

00:53:57.510 --> 00:54:18.109
[Yogi says, “He says, ‘When we fall in
love, why is there so much heartache and grief?'”]

00:54:18.109 --> 00:54:18.369
Shri Mataji: Because you fall.

00:54:18.369 --> 00:54:18.640
Shri Mataji: You should rise.

00:54:18.640 --> 00:54:19.369
What’s another? Behind that. Somebody else

00:54:19.369 --> 00:54:21.580
[A man asks, “What happens after death?”]

00:54:21.580 --> 00:54:23.800
[Yogi: “Life after death he is asking.”]

00:54:23.800 --> 00:54:28.710
Shri Mataji: Yes, that is all right. You see,
I must have given lots of lectures on that

00:54:28.710 --> 00:54:34.660
point also. You’d be amazed. I must have
spoken I don’t know how many times, but

00:54:34.660 --> 00:54:40.400
at least there are four thousand tapes of
Mine and this subject also I have dealt with,

00:54:40.400 --> 00:54:47.440
but what I’m saying today is let us be in
the present. Why worry about the death? All

00:54:47.440 --> 00:54:49.780
right?
Is there anybody else? Yes, please.

00:54:49.780 --> 00:55:05.330
[A man asks, “What is the connection between
sex and Kundalini and would you say something

00:55:05.330 --> 00:55:05.830
about AIDS?”]

00:55:05.830 --> 00:55:10.380
Shri Mataji: Now, here you see this red chakra
is the Mooladhara chakra, is the first chakra,

00:55:10.380 --> 00:55:16.550
is of our innocence. Our innocence is never
lost. We may do anything what we like. It

00:55:16.550 --> 00:55:25.170
is covered like a sky can be covered with
lots of clouds. Kundalini is placed above,

00:55:25.170 --> 00:55:32.290
you see. So it has nothing to do with sex
because this is the last centre, the seventh

00:55:32.290 --> 00:55:38.349
center or the first center, whatever you may
call it, is the centre of excretion, of sex

00:55:38.349 --> 00:55:43.270
and everything. It has nothing to do with
sex. On the contrary, you become innocent

00:55:43.270 --> 00:55:50.840
like a child. When the Kundalini is rising,
all these actions of excretion stop completely

00:55:50.840 --> 00:55:58.260
and all the force of our innocence helps the
Kundalini to rise. It has no relationship

00:55:58.260 --> 00:55:59.640
at all, at that time.

00:55:59.640 --> 00:56:05.440
But I don’t say there’s something wrong
in all these things, but there has to be some

00:56:05.440 --> 00:56:11.650
sanctity about it, should be some sense. People
become extremely sensible after marriage,

00:56:11.650 --> 00:56:13.480
even about sex life.

00:56:13.480 --> 00:56:22.200
AIDS have been cured with Sahaja Yoga, no
doubt, no doubt. But the patients of AIDS

00:56:22.200 --> 00:56:29.130
are of two categories I’ve seen. One who
think they are martyrs, they have achieved

00:56:29.130 --> 00:56:38.700
a great, you see, some sort of a big country
or some sort of a thing like that. They feel

00:56:38.700 --> 00:56:45.060
very enthusiastic about it. And the another
kind are the ones who don’t want to live,

00:56:45.060 --> 00:56:49.890
absolutely, just they don’t want to live.
So there are two types of people who suffer

00:56:49.890 --> 00:56:55.420
from AIDS mostly. Very few you find they are
in between. So we got rid [clarify: change

00:56:55.420 --> 00:57:01.700
to “cured”] of five of them, somehow,
in Australia. Out of them, one was a married

00:57:01.700 --> 00:57:08.550
couple who got all right and one fellow who
got all right this is nine years back, he’s

00:57:08.550 --> 00:57:13.060
still all right. But two of them, again went
to some funny habits or I don’t know what

00:57:13.060 --> 00:57:18.670
they did. The father of one of them told Me
that, “Mother, You just forgive them.”

00:57:18.670 --> 00:57:23.240
And I don’t know what happened. They again
got back their AIDS.

00:57:23.240 --> 00:57:30.200
So it’s a very difficult area in which one
has to work because they cannot be convinced

00:57:30.200 --> 00:57:35.460
that they can be cured and some of them think
that, “What’s wrong?” You see, this

00:57:35.460 --> 00:57:40.630
is the greatest mantra of the West, “What’s
wrong?” You tell them anything. “What’s

00:57:40.630 --> 00:57:45.340
wrong?” These punks were putting some sort
of horrible colors or they are becoming blind.

00:57:45.340 --> 00:57:51.480
I told them, “Why do you put these horrible
colors on your head because you are becoming

00:57:51.480 --> 00:57:56.980
blind?” “What’s wrong?” I said, “You’ll
become blind.” He said, “What’s wrong?”

00:57:56.980 --> 00:58:02.030
I mean, I just don’t know how to answer
these people. Very queer, isn’t it? They

00:58:02.030 --> 00:58:07.040
are bent upon destroying themselves. They
like to destroy. You see, the people just

00:58:07.040 --> 00:58:12.450
want to destroy themselves. I don’t know
from where this idea of destruction has come.

00:58:12.450 --> 00:58:19.910
Instead of constructing yourself, enjoying
life, anything, looking to higher goals, they

00:58:19.910 --> 00:58:27.830
always see to something filthy, dirty, something
that is absolutely inhuman, subhuman. I don’t

00:58:27.830 --> 00:58:32.200
know how these tendencies have grown.

00:58:32.200 --> 00:58:43.700
Cancer, of course, many types of cancers have
been cured. We have blood cancer. Some of

00:58:43.700 --> 00:58:48.220
them were told that you’ll die within one
month’s time because doctors are now honest

00:58:48.220 --> 00:58:53.150
and they give a certificate you are going
to die after one month. This happened about

00:58:53.150 --> 00:59:00.349
with one gentleman at least eight or nine
years back. He’s still all right and there

00:59:00.349 --> 00:59:04.970
are three of them like that who are perfectly
all right. There’s so many who have been

00:59:04.970 --> 00:59:13.030
cured, so many. So this cure takes place,
but also if you see, if God has any common

00:59:13.030 --> 00:59:18.349
sense, why should he cure people who are not
going to give light? Most of them they want

00:59:18.349 --> 00:59:27.260
to get cured and get lost. They are cured
to give light to others. We don’t repair

00:59:27.260 --> 00:59:31.230
lamps which are not going to give light. But
in compassion, I think God does that.

00:59:31.230 --> 00:59:34.150
[A man starts to ask a question.]

00:59:34.150 --> 00:59:39.099
Yogi: “He wants to get realization.”

00:59:39.099 --> 00:59:44.830
Shri Mataji: All right. Now, there’s somebody
else. Now, one more. Now, one more question.

00:59:44.830 --> 00:59:44.869
Now…

00:59:44.869 --> 00:59:45.070
[A woman asks a question.]

00:59:45.070 --> 00:59:45.430
[Yogi: “She is asking about the psychic
phenomenon, one thing. And she says when she

00:59:45.430 --> 01:00:04.910
is in nature, she is more at peace with herself,
her relationship.”]

01:00:04.910 --> 01:00:23.470
Shri Mataji: That’s, you see, nothing so
great. If you are in nature, anybody can feel

01:00:23.470 --> 01:00:32.670
peaceful. Or it’s like when you have everything
fine, you enjoy it, isn’t it? But when you

01:00:32.670 --> 01:00:53.680
are in Philadelphia, you should feel peaceful.
Or in New York. It’s also more difficult.

01:00:53.680 --> 01:01:05.230
[A woman asks: “When the Kundalini arises
is it in a state which stays with you all

01:01:05.230 --> 01:01:05.380
the time.]

01:01:05.380 --> 01:01:05.530
[The yogi repeats the question to Shri Mataji
in Hindi.]

01:01:05.530 --> 01:01:08.220
Shri Mataji: That’s a good question. You
see, it is like a connection as I said. Some

01:01:08.220 --> 01:01:17.340
people, once they get connection, they are
connected and they grow faster and faster.

01:01:17.340 --> 01:01:23.109
But some people have a loose connection also.
So is best is to get your connection done

01:01:23.109 --> 01:01:31.000
properly. From that distance, all right.

01:01:31.000 --> 01:01:38.349
[A woman asks a question.]

01:01:38.349 --> 01:01:42.950
[Yogi asks the woman, “What’s the difference
between …?”]

01:01:42.950 --> 01:01:43.730
[The woman continues.]

01:01:43.730 --> 01:01:46.849
[Yogi: “Who are Hare Krishna? Oh here, Sahaja
Yoga and Hare Krishna.”]

01:01:46.849 --> 01:01:47.630
Shri Mataji: Tremendous.

01:01:47.630 --> 01:01:54.400
Shri Mataji: You see, in India everybody says
to each other, when they wish, “Hare Krishna”

01:01:54.400 --> 01:02:05.099
or “Hare Ram.” Are they all going to go
to God? Just understand, these are words.

01:02:05.099 --> 01:02:16.540
Get out of the webs of words. Shabtah ja alam
(check spelling) Get out of the webs of words.

01:02:16.540 --> 01:02:28.450
All right? Also, get out of books. Too much
reading books, also makes you mad. I tell

01:02:28.450 --> 01:02:33.560
you, it’s really true. Kabira has said Pari,
pari pandita mura … ? [check spelling],

01:02:33.560 --> 01:02:35.280
means “By reading too much, even the learned
became stupid.”

01:02:35.280 --> 01:02:35.440
Shri Mataji: Now, one.

01:02:35.440 --> 01:02:36.060
[A woman asks, “How do you know if your
center is blocked?”]

01:02:36.060 --> 01:02:36.300
Shri Mataji: What’s it?

01:02:36.300 --> 01:02:45.380
[Yogi: “How do you know if your center is
blocked?”]

01:02:45.380 --> 01:02:50.770
Shri Mataji: I or you?

01:02:50.770 --> 01:02:55.849
[Yogi: “No, you. She.”]

01:02:55.849 --> 01:03:02.450
Shri Mataji: You will know on your fingertips.
Alright? In English language there are certain

01:03:02.450 --> 01:03:08.450
things very good “on your fingertips.”
But also English language is little limited

01:03:08.450 --> 01:03:15.490
for spirituality because spirit is “Atma,”
is the Spirit I am talking about. “spirit”

01:03:15.490 --> 01:03:23.010
is a dead spirit, dead body. It is also alcohol,
you see. Out of these three, I am talking

01:03:23.010 --> 01:03:30.560
about which spirit people ask Me. So but fingertips
you know.

01:03:30.560 --> 01:03:41.130
[A woman asks a question.]

01:03:41.130 --> 01:03:56.960
[Yogi repeats the question in Hindi. “The
number one chakra is weak.”]

01:03:56.960 --> 01:04:08.220
Shri Mataji: It’s a little private question.
I’ll answer you privately. Alright?

01:04:08.220 --> 01:04:10.880
Who else is there?

01:04:10.880 --> 01:04:13.920
[Yogi: “Yes, go ahead and ask.”]

01:04:13.920 --> 01:04:15.450
Shri Mataji: Now, so many are there still.

01:04:15.450 --> 01:04:26.280
[A man say: “If you, yourself, have a question,
what question would you hope somebody would

01:04:26.280 --> 01:04:34.510
ask you that nobody ever asks you?”]

01:04:34.510 --> 01:04:46.060
[Yogi repeats the question in Hindi. “He
says, if you had a question that nobody else

01:04:46.060 --> 01:04:56.060
had asked you, what would be that question?”]

01:04:56.060 --> 01:05:00.460
Shri Mataji: I didn’t follow

01:05:00.460 --> 01:05:04.589
[Yogi to man: “What are you trying to…?]

01:05:04.589 --> 01:05:05.089
[The man says, “I can ask a different way.”]
[Yogi: “Yes.”]

01:05:05.089 --> 01:05:06.650
[The man asks, “If you are in the light,
what question do you think the light…”]

01:05:06.650 --> 01:05:09.160
[Yogi: “He’s saying, ‘If you’re in
the light, what question would the light have?'”]

01:05:09.160 --> 01:05:17.150
Shri Mataji: Light has no question. It has
to give light. How can it have question? You

01:05:17.150 --> 01:05:26.140
are already enlightened, so better give light
to others. Yes, please?

01:05:26.140 --> 01:05:31.430
[A man asks a question.]

01:05:31.430 --> 01:05:34.070
[Yogi repeats the question: “How can we
improve our psychic or spiritual experience?”]

01:05:34.070 --> 01:05:39.240
Shri Mataji: That’s what I’m saying. That’s
what I’m saying. First you get your realization

01:05:39.240 --> 01:05:43.880
and then you have to go to our centers and
you’ll be amazed. We have many here who

01:05:43.880 --> 01:05:48.520
are realized souls. They look like you, but
you can see the glow on their faces.

01:05:48.520 --> 01:05:56.300
You see, now this Marathi song is such a difficult
one, even a Sanskrit song. How can these people

01:05:56.300 --> 01:06:01.410
from America sing it? Just tell Me. Yes, sir?

01:06:01.410 --> 01:06:04.740
[A man asks a question.]

01:06:04.740 --> 01:06:13.420
[Yogi: “Shri Mataji, is the spiritual heart
and the physical heart the same?]

01:06:13.420 --> 01:06:18.880
Shri Mataji: Yes. In the physical heart resides
the spiritual heart.

01:06:18.880 --> 01:06:26.880
Shri Mataji: Now, I think we have had too
many. You want to ask?

01:06:26.880 --> 01:06:28.119
[Yogi: “Do you have a question?”]

01:06:28.119 --> 01:06:29.990
Shri Mataji: She has already asked. Now, who
else has not asked, can ask.

01:06:29.990 --> 01:06:30.490
Please.

01:06:30.490 --> 01:06:31.940
[A woman asks a question.]

01:06:31.940 --> 01:06:36.760
[Yogi: “What is the soul?”]

01:06:36.760 --> 01:06:44.349
Shri Mataji: That also is another big question
for which I have a big tape which you can

01:06:44.349 --> 01:06:47.970
go through and see for yourself. It will take
another lecture, all right

01:06:47.970 --> 01:06:51.330
who else?

01:06:51.330 --> 01:06:59.730
[A man asks a question.]

01:06:59.730 --> 01:07:09.820
[Yogi repeats the question in Hindi.]

01:07:09.820 --> 01:07:17.940
Cataract ne. One person has been, but, you
see, this cataract is something dead. If anything

01:07:17.940 --> 01:07:23.839
that’s dead, we cannot do it because it’s
dead. But anything that is living and in a

01:07:23.839 --> 01:07:28.650
jeopardy can be cured. All right?

01:07:28.650 --> 01:07:38.000
One [unclear killed], but he was a child.
He was a child. Madame, you’ve asked a question,

01:07:38.000 --> 01:07:44.510
all right. Now what’s that? There.

01:07:44.510 --> 01:07:48.160
[A man starts to ask a question.]

01:07:48.160 --> 01:07:49.810
Shri Mataji: No, no, no. Not you. She’s
there at the side.

01:07:49.810 --> 01:07:54.599
[A woman asks a question concerning mental
disorder.]

01:07:54.599 --> 01:07:58.200
[Yogi repeats the question in Hindi.]

01:07:58.200 --> 01:08:06.950
Ah, of course, of course, of course. Schizophrenia,
all kinds, epilepsy, lunacy, yes, of course.

01:08:06.950 --> 01:08:13.580
Depression. Of course. Yes, yes, yes. Works
out, works out.

01:08:13.580 --> 01:08:18.219
[A man starts to ask a question.]

01:08:18.219 --> 01:08:21.429
Shri Mataji: You’ve asked a question already.

01:08:21.429 --> 01:08:22.150
[A man asks a question.]

01:08:22.150 --> 01:08:31.279
[Yogi: “Person who have birth defects, who
don’t have complete bodies, can they become

01:08:31.279 --> 01:08:31.929
whole?”]

01:08:31.929 --> 01:08:39.119
Shri Mataji: Yes, some can be. Not all. But
it’s not important, you see. It’s not

01:08:39.119 --> 01:08:45.359
a hospital. I’m just a, it’s not a hospital.
With your own power, you cure yourself. The

01:08:45.359 --> 01:08:53.529
main attention should be on the spirit, not
on the body so much. Some people have definitely

01:08:53.529 --> 01:09:02.880
have been cured. His sister-in-law was spastic.
She got cured, but some are not because they

01:09:02.880 --> 01:09:11.789
just don’t do it. They don’t follow it
and what important thing is that don’t put

01:09:11.789 --> 01:09:18.549
your attention to the physical side [unclear:
so much?], or to the mental side. Just now,

01:09:18.549 --> 01:09:27.799
we have to achieve our spiritual goal. Yes,
please?

01:09:27.799 --> 01:09:39.719
[A man asks a question.]

01:09:39.719 --> 01:09:55.170
[Yogi: “He’s asking a lot of questions
are relating to suffering and then he’s

01:09:55.170 --> 01:10:00.280
asking about Jesus, how He suffered and rose
again from the dead.”]

01:10:00.280 --> 01:10:07.059
Shri Mataji: Sufferings are because of ignorance.
That’s all I’ll say in a small sentence.

01:10:07.059 --> 01:10:13.679
All right? And if you want to get out of it,
you get the knowledge. Knowledge on your central

01:10:13.679 --> 01:10:14.499
nervous system.

