[Yogi: “Shall we have the realization now?”]

01:10:18.420 --> 01:10:24.150
Shri Mataji: Now, I think we should stop it
because you have asked too many questions

01:10:24.150 --> 01:10:32.840
and I’ve answered them. Actually, you see,
as I told you, it’s a mental acrobat and

01:10:32.840 --> 01:10:40.639
I can answer most of the questions very well,
but it is of no use as far as Sahaja Yoga

01:10:40.639 --> 01:10:45.929
is concerned. Mostly I’ve seen people who
ask too many questions walk off. They just

01:10:45.929 --> 01:10:48.630
come here to ask questions and then just walk
off.

01:10:48.630 --> 01:10:57.889
So, again, I request you to put your attention
on yourself and on your own spirit and on

01:10:57.889 --> 01:11:03.329
your own benevolence. Now don’t think of
anything else. You might have read a lot,

01:11:03.329 --> 01:11:06.610
you might have known a lot and it’s all
right. You are worried about the whole world.

01:11:06.610 --> 01:11:11.099
It doesn’t matter. Now, please this is a
time, you give some time to yourself and you

01:11:11.099 --> 01:11:21.239
worry about yourself. So now we can have our
Realization.

01:11:21.239 --> 01:11:39.510
Those who don’t want to have Realization
should leave the hall because it’s civil.

01:11:39.510 --> 01:11:50.119
Others who want to have, please be seated.
You’re welcome and I’m sure it will all

01:11:50.119 --> 01:11:51.909
work out.

01:11:51.909 --> 01:11:56.559
Another request is that you have to take out
your shoes for a short time because this Mother

01:11:56.559 --> 01:12:01.429
Earth helps us a lot.

01:12:01.429 --> 01:12:24.199
Now, whatever we are going to do it, that
is for only tonight. You don’t have to repeat

01:12:24.199 --> 01:12:29.329
it again, so there’s no need to write, there’s
nothing to worry, just you have to see that

01:12:29.329 --> 01:12:32.909
it works out.

01:12:32.909 --> 01:12:46.920
Only thing, I have to make a humble request
that during meditation don’t walk out or

01:12:46.920 --> 01:12:53.420
don’t disturb.

01:12:53.420 --> 01:13:00.369
As you know, there are two powers, one on
the left and the right, two sympathetic nervous

01:13:00.369 --> 01:13:12.800
systems. So we put both our feet apart from
each other, left and right. Left is the power

01:13:12.800 --> 01:13:16.949
of desire.

01:13:16.949 --> 01:13:35.749
Please be seated. Will you please be seated?
No, you have to sit down, please. [Shri Mataji

01:13:35.749 --> 01:13:46.780
speaks in Hindi.] All right.

01:13:46.780 --> 01:13:53.570
Left hand towards Me on your lap. I’ve again
said that you have to be comfortable, but

01:13:53.570 --> 01:14:01.929
you should not slouch. You have to be comfortable.
Please put left hand towards Me. If anything

01:14:01.929 --> 01:14:07.719
tight on your stomach [Shri Mataji speaks
in Hindi.].

01:14:07.719 --> 01:14:16.239
If you don’t want to attend you can go out.

01:14:16.239 --> 01:14:28.880
Now, you have your left hand towards Me, which
is symbolic that you want to have, or you

01:14:28.880 --> 01:14:36.630
desire to have, your Self Realization. That
you have to keep all the time like that. If

01:14:36.630 --> 01:14:42.699
you have anything tight here or tight here,
little bit loosen it. If you are comfortable,

01:14:42.699 --> 01:14:47.280
it is all right, if you are comfortable. Main
thing is you should not be uncomfortable with

01:14:47.280 --> 01:14:48.800
anything.

01:14:48.800 --> 01:14:57.389
Now, we use this right hand for action, means
nourishing our centers. We have to nourish

01:14:57.389 --> 01:15:03.690
our centers ourselves. So now, put your right
hand on your heart. You can put it under the

01:15:03.690 --> 01:15:12.139
coat; need not be under the sweater, but under
the coat. Now, in the heart, just now keep

01:15:12.139 --> 01:15:20.440
your eyes open so you can see what you have
to do. In the heart resides the spirit. Now,

01:15:20.440 --> 01:15:28.199
if you become the spirit, in the light of
the spirit, you are your own guide, you are

01:15:28.199 --> 01:15:37.440
your own master, so take your right hand on
the left hand side of your abdomen on the

01:15:37.440 --> 01:15:46.199
upper portion, we are only working on the
left hand side. This is the centre of your

01:15:46.199 --> 01:15:50.420
mastery created by the great prophets.

01:15:50.420 --> 01:15:58.869
Now take your hand in the lower portion of
your abdomen on the left hand side. This is

01:15:58.869 --> 01:16:13.199
the center of Pure Divine Knowledge. Surprisingly,
it is here, pure, divine knowledge.

01:16:13.199 --> 01:16:22.420
Then raise your hand again on top of your
abdomen, the upper portion on the left hand

01:16:22.420 --> 01:16:29.289
side and press it hard.

01:16:29.289 --> 01:16:41.809
Now raise your hand again on the heart.

01:16:41.809 --> 01:16:55.579
Now put your hand in the corner of your neck
and your shoulder and turn your head to your

01:16:55.579 --> 01:17:08.229
right. This center goes into jeopardy when
you feel guilty. I’ll tell about this later

01:17:08.229 --> 01:17:09.519
on.

01:17:09.519 --> 01:17:19.670
Now raise your hand on your forehead across
and put down your head. This is the center

01:17:19.670 --> 01:17:24.469
for forgiving everyone, even without thinking
about them.

01:17:24.469 --> 01:17:33.969
Now take your right hand on the backside of
your head. Push back your head and here you

01:17:33.969 --> 01:17:42.880
have to ask forgiveness from the Divine Power
for your own satisfaction.

01:17:42.880 --> 01:17:50.219
Now the last centre is, stretch your palm
and put the center of your palm on top of

01:17:50.219 --> 01:17:59.119
your fontanelle bone area which was a soft
bone in your childhood and put down your head.

01:17:59.119 --> 01:18:06.999
Here push back your fingers this is very important
so there’s a good pressure on your scalp.

01:18:06.999 --> 01:18:17.789
Now, please put down your head and move your
scalp seven times; clockwise slowly. Please

01:18:17.789 --> 01:18:24.400
put down your heads. Put down your heads.
Can do it better. Put down your heads and

01:18:24.400 --> 01:18:31.849
push back your fingers, very important it
is. Push back. Now, put down your head and

01:18:31.849 --> 01:18:38.860
push back your fingers so there’s a good
pressure on your scalp. That’s all we have

01:18:38.860 --> 01:18:39.739
to do.

01:18:39.739 --> 01:18:50.010
Now, there are three conditions which I’ll
tell you, which are very simple ones. The

01:18:50.010 --> 01:18:58.880
first condition is that you all have to be
absolutely confident that you’ll all get

01:18:58.880 --> 01:19:09.469
your Self Realization. Please take down your
hands. You all have to be absolutely confident

01:19:09.469 --> 01:19:25.010
that you will get your Self Realization tonight.
That means that you’re not to feel guilty

01:19:25.010 --> 01:19:38.449
at all. That means forget your past. Whatever
wrong you have done, whatever mistakes you

01:19:38.449 --> 01:19:52.229
have committed will be dissolved by this power
of Divine Love because it is the ocean of

01:19:52.229 --> 01:20:00.119
forgiveness. So you have to forgive yourself
and you don’t know when you feel guilty

01:20:00.119 --> 01:20:04.530
what happens. If you have committed mistakes,
it’s all right. After all, you are human

01:20:04.530 --> 01:20:11.030
beings, you are not gods. You face the mistakes,
finished of them. But what you do, you carry

01:20:11.030 --> 01:20:23.539
that here onto this centre here. Thus, you
get spondylitis, cervical cancer, angina or

01:20:23.539 --> 01:20:24.329
lethargic organs.

01:20:24.329 --> 01:20:32.050
So what’s the use of carrying this with
you all the time? For something that happened

01:20:32.050 --> 01:20:39.949
long time back you are carrying still. Please
know you are not guilty at all. At this moment

01:20:39.949 --> 01:20:53.510
you are not guilty at all. I assure you are
not guilty. Let the Kundalini judge you. You

01:20:53.510 --> 01:20:56.959
don’t judge yourself. Alright.

01:20:56.959 --> 01:21:11.209
The second condition is that you have to forgive
everyone without even thinking about it. You

01:21:11.209 --> 01:21:19.929
have to forgive everyone. Now, many people
say it’s difficult to forgive. Whether you

01:21:19.929 --> 01:21:26.269
forgive or you don’t forgive, you don’t
do anything. What do you do if you don’t

01:21:26.269 --> 01:21:31.449
forgive? But when you don’t forgive, then
you play into wrong hands and you torture

01:21:31.449 --> 01:21:37.030
yourself, while the person who has troubled
you or hurt you is happy. But you are torturing

01:21:37.030 --> 01:21:38.699
yourself all your life.

01:21:38.699 --> 01:21:47.320
Now, at this moment, this centre is very important
because if it is not all right the Kundalini

01:21:47.320 --> 01:21:57.769
won’t rise. And also the centre between
the optic chiasm, which is like this, is absolutely

01:21:57.769 --> 01:22:04.360
constricted. It won’t open, but when you
forgive, it opens. So, as it is, you have

01:22:04.360 --> 01:22:11.969
tortured yourself all your life by not forgiving
and at this important moment you lose the

01:22:11.969 --> 01:22:13.760
chance of your Self Realization.

01:22:13.760 --> 01:22:22.269
So, just forgive everything, everybody, everything,
even without thinking about them. We can say

01:22:22.269 --> 01:22:26.110
forgive them in general. Alright.

01:22:26.110 --> 01:22:34.199
In short, you have be pleasantly placed towards
yourself. Because you are human beings, you

01:22:34.199 --> 01:22:39.869
are at the epitome of evolution. You don’t
know what you are. So please don’t condemn

01:22:39.869 --> 01:22:45.489
yourself. Don’t, in any way, get angry with
yourself. It’s a very simple thing that

01:22:45.489 --> 01:22:49.360
will happen to you and you’ll be amazed
at your own greatness.

01:22:49.360 --> 01:22:58.449
So now, please put your left hand on your
left lap and also both the feet away from

01:22:58.449 --> 01:23:01.849
each other.

01:23:01.849 --> 01:23:12.010
Now, please put the right hand on your heart
and now close your eyes. You can take out

01:23:12.010 --> 01:23:22.479
your spectacles also because your eyesight
might improve. Now please put your right hand

01:23:22.479 --> 01:23:40.459
on your heart.

01:23:40.459 --> 01:23:50.880
Here you have to ask in your heart a question
which is very fundamental. You can call Me

01:23:50.880 --> 01:24:00.510
“Mother” or you can call Me “Shri Mataji.”
Please ask three times, “Mother, am I the

01:24:00.510 --> 01:24:14.429
Spirit?” Ask this question, “Mother, am
I the spirit?” three times. I have told

01:24:14.429 --> 01:24:22.150
you when you become the Spirit you become
your guide, your master.

01:24:22.150 --> 01:24:28.849
So now, please take your right hand to the
upper portion of your abdomen and press it

01:24:28.849 --> 01:24:42.599
hard. Here, you have to say, again three times,
ask a question which is very fundamental,

01:24:42.599 --> 01:25:09.780
“Mother, am I my own master?” Ask this
question three times.

01:25:09.780 --> 01:25:17.110
Now please take your right hand in the lower
portion of your abdomen. Here the center has

01:25:17.110 --> 01:25:31.090
got six petals, so you have to ask six times.
I must say, I cannot force pure, divine knowledge

01:25:31.090 --> 01:25:42.360
on you. You have to ask for it. So please
ask six times, “Mother, please give me Pure

01:25:42.360 --> 01:25:51.909
Divine Knowledge”, in your heart, everything
to be asked in your heart, “Mother, please

01:25:51.909 --> 01:26:04.999
give me Pure Divine Knowledge”

01:26:04.999 --> 01:26:23.760
Now, as soon as you ask for Pure Divine Knowledge,
the Kundalini starts rising. So we have to

01:26:23.760 --> 01:26:30.380
nourishes the higher centers with our full
self-confidence, so now raise your right hand

01:26:30.380 --> 01:26:41.699
to the upper portion of your abdomen, on the
left hand side and here you have to say with

01:26:41.699 --> 01:26:53.159
full self-confidence, “Mother, I am my own
master”, say ten times “Mother, I am my

01:26:53.159 --> 01:26:59.409
own master”.

01:26:59.409 --> 01:27:20.729
I’ve already told you that are not this
body, this mind, this ego, this conditionings

01:27:20.729 --> 01:27:30.590
but you are the pure Spirit, so please raise
your right hand on top of your heart and here

01:27:30.590 --> 01:27:49.590
you have to say 12 times, with full confidence,
“Mother, I am the pure Spirit”.

01:27:49.590 --> 01:27:55.079
Do not say any mantras or anything and don’t
try to concentrate, just leave your attention

01:27:55.079 --> 01:28:09.329
free, the Kundalini will push it, so you just
have to put no efforts about it. This All

01:28:09.329 --> 01:28:22.769
Pervading Power is the ocean of compassion,
is the ocean of knowledge, is the ocean of

01:28:22.769 --> 01:28:29.420
bliss and joy and above all is the ocean of
forgiveness, so whatever mistakes you might

01:28:29.420 --> 01:28:37.739
have committed are easily dissolved into this
power of ocean of forgiveness, so please forgive

01:28:37.739 --> 01:28:44.749
yourself, and raise your hand in the corner
of your neck and shoulder and turn your head

01:28:44.749 --> 01:28:51.590
to the right.

01:28:51.590 --> 01:29:01.229
This is the center which is very bad today,
I think that you feel guilty, so please say

01:29:01.229 --> 01:29:20.780
with full confidence “Mother, I am not guilty
at all”, please say it with full confidence,

01:29:20.780 --> 01:29:32.570
sixteen times you have to say, I’ve already
told you logically, wherever you forgive or

01:29:32.570 --> 01:29:37.139
you don’t forgive, you don’t do anything.
But if you don’t forgive then you play into

01:29:37.139 --> 01:29:44.619
wrong hands, especially at this moment, you
have to forgive because the center of Agnya

01:29:44.619 --> 01:29:50.789
is very constricted and won’t open and your
Kundalini won’t raise, so it is very important

01:29:50.789 --> 01:29:58.519
now that you have to forgive, so raise your
right hand on top of your forehead across,

01:29:58.519 --> 01:30:13.550
and please put down your head, here you have
to say
from your heart, not how many times “Mother,

01:30:13.550 --> 01:30:22.289
I forgive everyone in general”, don’t
think about it, just say it, please put down

01:30:22.289 --> 01:30:33.929
your head.

01:30:33.929 --> 01:31:02.969
Now, please take your right hand to the backside
of your head, and push back your head, here,

01:31:02.969 --> 01:31:08.760
without feeling guilty, without counting your
mistake, just for your satisfaction have to

01:31:08.760 --> 01:31:21.039
say “Oh, Divine Power, please forgive me
if I have done any mistakes knowingly or unknowingly”,

01:31:21.039 --> 01:31:31.070
“Oh, Divine Power, please forgive me if
I have done any mistakes knowingly or unknowingly”,

01:31:31.070 --> 01:31:52.340
say it from your heart, not how many times.
Please say it from

01:31:52.340 --> 01:31:59.789
your heart. Now, please stretch your palm
on your right hand and put the center of your

01:31:59.789 --> 01:32:10.449
palm on the fontanelle bone area, which was
the soft bone in your childhood. Now, this

01:32:10.449 --> 01:32:16.019
is important that you push back your fingers,
so there’s a good pressure on your scalp,

01:32:16.019 --> 01:32:24.939
now please put down your head, here again
I cannot force Sahaja Yoga on you, I cannot

01:32:24.939 --> 01:32:34.939
force Self Realization on you, so please move
your scalp seven times, clockwise, saying

01:32:34.939 --> 01:32:57.019
“Mother, please give me my self Realization”.

01:32:57.019 --> 01:33:26.130
Now, please take down your hand, open your
eyes, wear your glasses. Put both your hands

01:33:26.130 --> 01:33:38.309
towards me, like this, little higher. Now,
watch Me, without thinking, just watch Me

01:33:38.309 --> 01:33:42.559
without thinking.

01:33:42.559 --> 01:33:51.989
Now, put this right hand towards Me, like
this, bend your head, and see with your left

01:33:51.989 --> 01:33:57.949
hand if there’s a Cool Breeze coming out
of your fontanelle bone area, please bend

01:33:57.949 --> 01:34:08.309
your head; or maybe hot, please see that there’s
a cool or hot breeze coming out of your fontanelle

01:34:08.309 --> 01:34:14.590
bone area, please don’t put your hand on
top of your head, but away from it, and now

01:34:14.590 --> 01:34:34.920
see for yourself if there is a cool or hot
breeze coming from your head.

01:34:34.920 --> 01:34:48.039
Now, put your left hand towards Me, like this,
and again bend your head, and see with your

01:34:48.039 --> 01:34:54.050
right hand now if there is a cool or hot breeze
coming out of your head, sometimes it comes

01:34:54.050 --> 01:35:00.769
very far, some times closer. If it is hot,
means your have not forgiven or your are still

01:35:00.769 --> 01:35:10.489
feeling guilty, so please do it. All the heat
is coming out. Now see for yourself.

01:35:10.489 --> 01:35:19.349
Alright, now right hand towards Me, now and
with the left hand you’ll see for the last

01:35:19.349 --> 01:35:25.989
time, put down your head properly, and see
properly if there is a cool or hot breeze

01:35:25.989 --> 01:35:37.969
coming out of the your fontanelle bone area.
Now please put both the hands towards the

01:35:37.969 --> 01:35:47.239
sky, and push back your head, here you have
to ask any of these three questions, three

01:35:47.239 --> 01:35:56.059
times, “Mother, is this the Cool Breeze
of the Holy Ghost?”, or “Mother, is this

01:35:56.059 --> 01:36:03.360
the All Pervading Power of God’s Love, the
Ruh?” or “is it the Paramchaitanya?”,

01:36:03.360 --> 01:36:22.769
just ask any one of these questions three
times. Now, please put down your hands. All

01:36:22.769 --> 01:36:32.169
those who have felt cool or hot breeze on
their fingertips or palms, or in their hands

01:36:32.169 --> 01:36:38.600
or out of their fontanelle bone area, please
raise both your hands.
